Body: I asked those same questions yesterday in Telegram, team responded literally within a minute. Author: CarTaxi
Title: [ANN][ICO OVER-SUCCESS]CARTAXI:FIRST OPERATING CAR TOWING PLATFORM ON BLOCKCHAIN
Body: CarTaxi service uses modern technology, making it possible to call for road assistance of the same standard of service, wherever you might be. Now you can arrange a tow any time, anywhere. By combining geolocation with blockchain technologies and packaging them into an Uber-like interface familiar to users today, CarTaxi makes life simpler and easier for drivers around the world.  CarTaxi is already operationally active and functioning fully in Russia, where the app has become #1. Full-scale testing is being conducted to scale the service up globally. Also our offices in San Antonio and Hong Kong are actively connecting partners—i.e., tow truck owners—to our system. Connecting each new region through our partner system appears to be the best approach. It has proved itself well with the worldwide Uber service, so CarTaxi chose precisely this approach.
